{"tid":1429880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇武黃大仙】  D18黨媒PAGE","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:31:48.000Z","uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c81f3a2338fdc8912b0df2973329dcc09d670980","tid":1429880,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WongTaiSinLocals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWongTaiSinLocals%2F&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a3d9821f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WongTaiSinLocals/</a><br />\n哩個PAGE係撐警<br />\n話雷射筆係攻擊性武器<br />\n個PAGE有電話 大家識做啦<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\nD18 - 黃大仙友<br />\n4小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n觀星筆雷射可傷人應正視<br />\n<br />\n激光筆，或觀星筆，其實使用了有殺傷力的激光，隨時可用作&ldquo;襲擊武器&rdquo;， 對人體造成傷害及失明。即使較低能量的激光筆，如果直接照射眼睛超過10秒，可傷害視網膜，因此警方視作攻擊武器處理絕對正確。<br />\n<br />\n激光的危險程度一直備受媒體關注，蘋果日報、英國廣播公司ＢＢＣ及美國一視力保護中心也曾就激光筆所帶來的安全威脅作出報導。香港機電工程署亦有發生激光產品安全指引和分類。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報於2015年＜＜高危激光筆 1秒射盲眼＞＞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/&hellip;/&hellip;/article/20150516/19149634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F%E2%80%A6%2Farticle%2F20150516%2F19149634&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=4eb3f1f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F%E2%80%A6%2Farticle%2F20150516%2F19149634&h=545eb6ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/&hellip;/&hellip;/article/20150516/19149634</a><br />\n<br />\n美國Patty Vision Centers＜＜Can Laser Pointers Hurt Your Eyes?＞＞<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pattyvisioncenters.com/&hellip;/can-laser-pointers-hur&hellip;/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pattyvisioncenters.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fcan-laser-pointers-hur%E2%80%A6%2F&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=eb497a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pattyvisioncenters.com/&hellip;/can-laser-pointers-hur&hellip;/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港機電工程署激光產品安全指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.emsd.gov.hk/&hellip;/safety_guidelines_for_&hellip;/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emsd.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fsafety_guidelines_for_%E2%80%A6%2Findex.html&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=c238a9de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.emsd.gov.hk/&hellip;/safety_guidelines_for_&hellip;/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司ＢＢＣ於２０１６年＜＜Lasers should be classed as offensive weapons - pilots' union＞＞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-35580261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-35580261&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=953e317b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-35580261&h=d551abbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-35580261</a><br />\n<br />\n#黃大仙 #黃大仙友<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nWebsite ▸ <a href=\"http://www.d18hk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.d18hk.com&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=4c076e3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.d18hk.com</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">WhatsApp ▸ 6859 6358</span></span></strong><br />\nInstagram ▸ @d18hk<br />\nYouTube ▸ d18hk"},{"pid":"2f128df3ca50956f5eeaf6cfd39d91ce7c0c52ff","tid":1429880,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52749356b3f95a8445cbb0723cc3cc197e6cb520","tid":1429880,"uid":835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor